-Consideration of the proposal (register 3902) of Councillor São Silveirinha, regarding the above-mentioned subject, which is transcribed below:-" Considering Annex R.5 (Regulation for the Use and Operation of the Cultural Centre of Campo Maior) of the Regulatory Code of the Municipality of Campo Maior, in number 197 of the II series of the Diário da República, dated 12/10/2017, I propose:  - that the prices to be charged for the following initiatives and activities to be carried out during the month of March of the year two thousand and twenty-three are:
-06/03 – Theater "Ao Crescer Quero Ser" – Free;
-03/07 – Theater "Gabi, The World Needs You" – Free;
-09/03 – Theater "In the Language of Camões" – Free;
-Day 10/03 – Theater "In the Language of Camões" – Free;
-Day 11/03 – Theater – Vagina Monologues – €6,320, with 30% discount + VAT – €5.00;
-03/17 – Theater "Uma História Lusitana" – Free;
-Day 18/03 – Theater "A Sementeira" – €3,540, with 30% discount + VAT – €3,00;
-Day 19/03 – Theater "Egresso do Passado" – €3,540, with 30% discount + VAT – €3.00;
-Day 26/03 – Theater "O Sítio do Pica Pau Amarelo" – €3,540, with 30% discount + VAT – €3,00;
-THE CHAMBER UNANIMOUSLY DECIDED TO APPROVE THE PROPOSAL OF COUNCILOR SÃO SILVEIRINHA, REGARDING THE PRICE OF TICKETS FOR THE CAMPO MAIOR CULTURAL CENTER (MARCH 2023).

segments.text_pt:
-ANTECIPAÇÃO DO DIA DA REUNIÃO DE CÂMARA DE 20 PARA 13 DE ABRIL DE 2022:
-Apreciação da proposta (registo 4727) do senhor presidente, referente ao assunto em epígrafe, que a seguir se transcreve:-“Considerando o Regimento da Câmara Municipal de Campo Maior no que refere à realização das reuniões ordinárias;
-Considerando os compromissos assumidos anteriormente pelo Presidente da câmara para o dia vinte de abril de corrente ano;
-Considerando que durante o mês de abril ter-se-á que realizar a assembleia municipal, para aprovação dos Documentos de Prestações de Contas, referente ao ano de 2021;
-Considerando a falta de prazo que se verifica entre a última reunião do Executivo e o dia 29/04/2020, para marcação da assembleia municipal, proponho que:
-a segunda reunião do mês de abril seja antecipada para o dia 13 do mesmo mês”.
-A CÂMARA DELIBEROU, POR UNANIMIDADE, APROVAR A PROPOSTA DO SENHOR PRESIDENTE E ANTECIPAR A REUNIÃO DO DIA 20 PARA 13 DE ABRIL DE 2022.

segments.text_en:
-ANTICIPATION OF THE DAY OF THE TOWN HALL MEETING FROM APRIL 20 TO 13, 2022:
-Consideration of the proposal (register 4727) of the President, regarding the subject above, which is transcribed below:-"Considering the Rules of Procedure of the Municipality of Campo Maior with regard to the holding of ordinary meetings;
-Considering the commitments previously made by the Mayor for the twentieth of April of this year;
-Considering that during the month of April, the municipal assembly will have to be held, for the approval of the Accountability Documents, for the year 2021;
-Considering the lack of deadline that exists between the last meeting of the Executive and 29/04/2020, for scheduling the municipal assembly, I propose that:
-the second meeting of the month of April is brought forward to the 13th of the same month".
-THE CHAMBER UNANIMOUSLY DECIDED TO APPROVE THE PRESIDENT'S PROPOSAL AND BRING FORWARD THE MEETING FROM APRIL 20 TO 13, 2022.
